<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>纽约时报 &amp;gt; 美国 &amp;gt; 政治</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/spotlight/on-politics</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 08 May 2026 21:19:21 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>我们的记者在万斯 2028 年编码之旅期间在爱荷华州看到了什么</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/08/us/politics/jd-vance-iowa-2028.html</link><description>副总统来到该州为弱势的众议院共和党人做竞选演讲，也许还为潜在的总统竞选奠定了一些基础。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 May 2026 21:19:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/08/us/politics/jd-vance-iowa-2028.html</guid></item><item><title>密歇根州好斗的民主党参议院初选升温</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/06/us/politics/michigan-senate-primary-democrats.html</link><description>攻击四起，著名的民主党人正在选边站队，战斗才刚刚开始。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 May 2026 22:28:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/06/us/politics/michigan-senate-primary-democrats.html</guid></item><item><title>五月的初选将考验特朗普对共和党的影响力</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/04/us/politics/may-primary-elections-trump-republicans.html</link><description>一系列共和党竞选将考验他对党的控制力。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 21:19:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/04/us/politics/may-primary-elections-trump-republicans.html</guid></item><item><title>缅因州参议院竞选的实际情况如何</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/01/us/politics/maine-senate-primary-election.html</link><description>该州是美国参议院最高竞选之一，反建制情绪十分明显。但参议员苏珊·柯林斯也有一些优势。</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 May 2026 21:32:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/01/us/politics/maine-senate-primary-election.html</guid></item><item><title>最高法院通过投票权法案的裁决改变了美国的政治版图</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/29/us/politics/redistricting-maps-supreme-court-voting.html</link><description>双方现在都在努力适应新的投票权格局。</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Apr 2026 21:21:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/29/us/politics/redistricting-maps-supreme-court-voting.html</guid></item><item><title>从州长竞选到财富税提案，亿万富翁正在主导加州政治</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/27/us/politics/california-billionaires-tax-governor.html</link><description>在谢尔盖·布林（Sergey Brin）和汤姆·斯泰尔（Tom Steyer）之间，超级富豪正在努力引导国家的方向。</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Apr 2026 21:49:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/27/us/politics/california-billionaires-tax-governor.html</guid></item><item><title>中期选举临近时共和党可能采取的策略：负面竞选</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/24/us/politics/republicans-midterms-campaign.html</link><description>共和党人可能会在中期选举中采取一种久经考验的策略：采取消极态度。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Apr 2026 21:39:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/24/us/politics/republicans-midterms-campaign.html</guid></item><item><title>为什么弗吉尼亚州的新地图对民主党中期选举很重要，以及下一步是什么</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/22/us/politics/virginia-redistricting-map-democrats-midterms.html</link><description>现在注意力转向佛罗里达州和最高法院。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 21:00:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/22/us/politics/virginia-redistricting-map-democrats-midterms.html</guid></item><item><title>民主党人曾经痛恨不公正地划分选区。现在他们正在努力争取。</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/20/us/politics/virginia-gerrymandering-referendum.html</link><description>该党在弗吉尼亚州寻求额外的优势之际，该党在绘制政治地图上的党派思维发生了变化——领导人表示，这在很大程度上是因为特朗普总统的策略。</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Apr 2026 21:26:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/20/us/politics/virginia-gerrymandering-referendum.html</guid></item><item><title>缅因州选民在 2026 年参议院选举前的想法</title><link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/17/us/politics/maine-senate-election-collins-platner-mills.html</link><description>该州的读者向我们讲述了该州高风险的参议院竞选。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Apr 2026 22:40:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/17/us/politics/maine-senate-election-collins-platner-mills.html</guid></item></channel></rss>